Ran pore check on all MinION flow cells.

As a reminder, MinION flow cells have a maximum of 2048 pores, and warranty guarantees 800 pores.

|------------|--------------|------------|

| B024226909 | FBD36396     | 1528       |
| B024226802 | FBD09922     | 1428       |

Nice! All 5 MinION flow cells are well above warranty.
